      *                  * tivo                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cod-abi-sos-000  thru acc-cod-abi-sos-999    .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-key    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cod-abi-999.
