      *                  * Visualizzazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      50                   to   v-car                  .
           move      w-lpt-cod-abi-lin    to   v-lin                  .
           move      w-lpt-cod-abi-pos    to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-vis-lit-sos        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-cod-abi-sos-900.
